title: Gabby Petito Part 2 // Statements, Dispute, and Theories
description:
In this episode, we discuss ALL up-to-date information on Gabby Petito's ongoing case and also discuss the Moab Murders that occurred just before Gabby's disappearance in the same area she was last seen in.
